<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4747137>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 7. Record of Leptostylum oligothrix Gudin and Messas sp. nov. parasitising a caterpillar of Automeris naranja Schaus (Saturniidae). (a) Fifth instar of A. naranja at prepupal stage, just before collection. (b) Death of caterpillar. (c) Emergence of third-instar larvae of L. oligothrix sp. nov. and beginning of pupation. (d) Puparia of L. oligothrix sp. nov." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4747137/files/figure.png" .
